Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.42,0:01:10.72,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}進むことに飽きたの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:13.72,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}叶えても　叶うだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.72,0:01:18.68,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}夢はなぜこの手で　形を変えてくの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.68,0:01:24.73,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}教えて　どれくらい？　頑張れば辿り着くの…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.73,0:01:30.03,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}理想につぶれてた　私はもういない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.40,0:01:33.49,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}夢の先をリライト
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.49,0:01:36.70,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}掴みたいよ未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.70,0:01:44.08,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}君と声を重ねて　届けるの　もっと先へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:47.17,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}ひとりじゃ歩けない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.17,0:01:50.34,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}景色　君とみてみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.34,0:01:53.64,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}ひとりじゃ進めない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.64,0:01:56.26,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}直感を信じて生きてたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.26,0:01:59.35,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}夢の先の New World
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.35,0:02:02.60,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}聞こえていますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:06.52,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}この声が終わるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:10.40,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}君に伝え続けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.23,0:00:44.77,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}重寫夢想的續集
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.77,0:00:48.15,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}會聽到未來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.15,0:00:53.53,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}我們的聲音重疊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.53,0:01:02.29,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}送出的開場曲 飛向夢想吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.29,0:01:07.42,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}總是尋找平坦的路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.42,0:01:10.72,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}只會讓我厭倦前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:13.72,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}就算去實現 也只是完成
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.72,0:01:18.68,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}夢想為何會因為這隻手改變形態呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.68,0:01:24.73,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}請告訴我 還要努力多久才能到達
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.73,0:01:30.03,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}曾經只能仰視理想的我 已經改變
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.40,0:01:33.49,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}重寫夢想的延續
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.49,0:01:36.70,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}希望把握住未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.70,0:01:44.08,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}我們的聲音重疊 直抵更遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:47.17,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}一個人走不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.17,0:01:50.34,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}想和你一同欣賞美景
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.34,0:01:53.64,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}一個人無法前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.64,0:01:56.26,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}希望能追隨直覺活著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.26,0:01:59.35,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}夢想前方的新世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.35,0:02:02.60,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}你聽清楚了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:06.52,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}直到無法發聲為止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:10.40,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}我都會一直為你開口
Comment: 0,0:22:04.97,0:22:08.14,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,---------------------------ED「STAND BY YOU」------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.14,0:22:13.52,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}Stand by me, you did that
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.52,0:22:16.15,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}Stand by you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.36,0:22:26.08,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}気持ち伝えるのにいつも何故　こんなにも悩み
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.08,0:22:29.25,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}ゆらり揺れている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.25,0:22:36.00,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}本当は君が好きなのに　うらはらで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.00,0:22:39.67,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}上手く言えないよ　ねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.59,0:22:42.38,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}振り返れば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.84,0:22:45.55,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}君が映る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.64,0:22:49.31,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}目と目合わせ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.31,0:22:54.40,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}愛の歌　そう唄い出す
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.40,0:23:00.61,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}君にいつか届くまでね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.61,0:23:03.20,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}大事にしてたフィーリング
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.20,0:23:05.66,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}全部込めるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.66,0:23:10.66,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}ちゃんと受け止めてくれるよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.66,0:23:15.92,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}真夜中のラブソングで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.92,0:23:21.88,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}世界がちょっと変わってほしい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.88,0:23:27.26,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}そして君とsweetie　2人ぼっち
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.26,0:23:29.93,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}100ミリちょっとの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.93,0:23:32.02,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}隙間埋める
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.02,0:23:33.85,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}be with you
Comment: 0,0:22:08.14,0:22:13.52,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,Stand by me, you did that
Comment: 0,0:22:13.52,0:22:16.15,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,Stand by you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.36,0:22:26.08,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}只是表明心意 為什麼讓我如此煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.08,0:22:29.25,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}總是搖擺不定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.25,0:22:36.00,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}其實那麼喜歡你 卻言不由衷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.00,0:22:39.67,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}找不到合適的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.59,0:22:42.38,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}回首身後
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.84,0:22:45.55,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}眼中有了你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.64,0:22:49.31,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}我們四目相對
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.31,0:22:54.40,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}唱響這首愛之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.40,0:23:00.61,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}希望有一天你能聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.61,0:23:03.20,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}一直珍惜的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.20,0:23:05.66,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}都包含其中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.66,0:23:10.66,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}你一定會接受它吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.66,0:23:15.92,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}願這首午夜小情歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.92,0:23:21.88,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}可以讓世界稍微改變
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.88,0:23:27.26,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}然後與你甜甜蜜蜜 二人世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.26,0:23:29.93,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}十多公分的間隙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.93,0:23:32.02,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}全都被填滿
Comment: 0,0:23:32.02,0:23:33.85,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,be with you
